# configs/homepage/vars.yaml.example
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Homepage variable substitution — {{HOMEPAGE_VAR_X}} syntax
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Homepage reads HOMEPAGE_VAR_* values from the container's
# environment variables, which are passed in via docker-compose.yml
# from your .env file.
#
# Workflow:
#   1. Copy root .env.example → .env
#   2. Fill in all HOMEPAGE_VAR_* values in .env
#   3. docker compose up -d homepage
#
# Where to find each API key:
#   Jellyfin     → Dashboard → API Keys → + (new key)
#   Jellyseerr   → Settings → General → API Key
#   Radarr       → Settings → General → API Key
#   Sonarr       → Settings → General → API Key
#   Lidarr       → Settings → General → API Key
#   Prowlarr     → Settings → General → API Key
#   Bazarr       → Settings → General → API Key
#   qBittorrent  → password you set in WebUI Options
#
# LXC IP: the IP of CT302 on your Proxmox network (e.g. 10.10.40.32)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────